Happy National Matcha Day! 🍵✨ We’re celebrating in the sweetest way possible—with a limited-edition sip you won’t want to miss! 🤭💋

Introducing the Cherry Kiss Latte, our exclusive collab with @chachamatcha — available only this weekend through May 4, at the Too Faced x Cha Cha Matcha Kiss Café in Venice! 🍒💖😚

Inspired by our juicy Kissing Jelly Lip Oil in Cherry Pie 🍒❤️, this dreamy drink is packed with all the goodness:

🍵 4g ceremonial grade matcha
🍓 Swirled strawberries & cherries
🌱 Creamy oat milk
☁️ Finished with vegan cold foam

It’s bold, it’s beautiful, and it’s here for a good time—not a long time 😉 Come sip & shop before it’s gone! 😘 #toofaced #tfcrueltyfree #toofacedkisscafe

The Kiss Café is officially OPEN!! 😍💋💖 We had such a fun first day at @chachamatcha Venice with you all! 🍒🍵

We’ll be back tomorrow through Sunday for more sweet treats, fun giveaways, exclusive indulgences, and the most incredible lip-loving experience EVER! 🥰😘💕

Don’t forget, the first 100 customers tomorrow will receive a free goodie!! 🤩 See you there! 😚💘

#toofaced #tfcrueltyfree #toofacedkisscafe

We can’t wait to see you there! 😘
